{"id": "1394103326362308799", "channel_id": "1326453763355185215", "author_id": "289320818901778434", "author_name": "nikolazuli", "content": "discord added the feature to embed links into text a few years back. on mobile if you long press the blue text you can see the real link", "timestamp": "2025-07-13T23:48:54.192000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-07-13T23:49:38.430000+00:00"}
