{"id": "1394103693858574389", "channel_id": "1326453763355185215", "author_id": "507989103011168287", "author_name": "nightjar0928", "content": "You can tell they got hacked since this is now a bot (which is fairly easy to surmise from their messages) the fact that they have a nickname on here rather than their normal username means that they manually did that which isn't something a bot would do. Hence they were once *not* a bot and thus they probably got their account hacked and hijacked to use for this botting purpose.", "timestamp": "2025-07-13T23:50:21.810000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-07-13T23:50:36.279000+00:00", "reactions": [{"emoji": "🔥", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}]}
